---
title: Sesame Sriracha Beef Stir-Fry with Carrot Ribbons and Jasmine Rice
description: If you’ve never been too keen on carrots, we’ve found a pretty nifty trick that might just get you to think again about the vitamin A-rich veg. In this recipe, they’re shaved into ribbons and tossed with beef in a sesame, honey, and soy-based sauce that packs sweet and savory flavors. Paired with fluffy Jasmine rice, this is the sort simple weeknight stir-fry that will make your taste buds sing.
